{
  "texts": [
    "We compiled a set of entities based on the official ontologies that were used to annotate the entities in the original CRAFT corpus.",
    "To ensure that all of the objects retrieved from ontologies are, in fact, new, this list has been cross-checked against the original dataset's vocabulary.",
    "The results for each tag are as follows:",
    "-Protein foot_1: 2000 entities -Chemicals foot_2: 1200 entities -Taxonomy foot_3: 1000 entities -Gene foot_4: 1000 entities -Cell foot_5: 1000 entities -Sequence foot_6: 2646 entities.",
    "There are 8846 entities in total."
  ]
}